<p><span class="anchor" id="p26"></span><span class="c1">" فتاوى اللجنة الدائمة "</span> <span class="c2">(٦ / ١٣٠ – ١٣٦)</span><a href="#p26" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>